               <msContents>
                  <summary>Mǝ‘raf chants, ምዕራፍ፡</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="97v" facs="005">Fols 1r–97v</locus>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT3186Meeraf">Mǝʿrāf</title>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">ምዕራፍ፡ እምዮሐንስ፡ እስከ፡ ዮሐንስ። ቅዱስ፡ እግዚአብሔር፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሃያል፡ ቅዱስ፡ ሕያው፡ ዘኢይመውት፡ <gap reason="omitted"/> ለእግዚአብሔር፡ ምድር፡ በምልዓ፡ ይቤ፡ ዮሐንስ፡ ወውእቱ፡ ባህር፡ ሣረራ፡ ም፡ ወበአፍላግኒ፡ ውእቱ፡ አጽንዓ፡ ዘኅብረት፡ ወመኑ፡ ይቀውም፡ ውስተ፡ መካነ መቅደሱ፡ ም፡ ዘንጹሕ፡ ልቡ፡ ወንጹሕ፡ እደዊሁ፡ <gap reason="omitted"/></incipit>
                    <notatedMusic><desc>with musical notation</desc></notatedMusic>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.1"><locus from="6v" facs="011">Fols 6v and following</locus><title>Supplications</title></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.2"><locus from="18v" facs="023">Fols 18v and following</locus><title>chants for the season of the flower (Zämänä Ṣǝge)</title></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.3"><locus from="39r" facs="043">Fols 39r and following</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1113Anqasa">ʾAnqaṣa
                                                  bǝrhān</title></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.4"><locus from="50r" facs="054">Fols 50r and following</locus><title>chants for Lent</title></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.5"><locus from="82r" facs="086">Fols 82r and following</locus><title>Homily called “Word of Blessing (Qalä Bäräkät) from our father, Yarǝd”</title></msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1.6"><locus from="89v" facs="094">Fols 89v and following</locus><title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT2509Weddas">Wǝddāse
                                                  Māryām</title></msItem>
